author: Kruggsmash
description:
*An edited, illustrated and narrated playthrough of the game Dwarf Fortress*

 We're back in Failedplans today to see what those goblins can muster in the new siege update! I have heard tales of all sorts of new goblin tricks and hope to see some today! Battering rams? Siege engineer trolls? Should be an interesting time!

Music by Ivan Duch: https://ivanduch.com/

Intro & End tunes by Topher Anselmo: https://topheranselmo.com/

Illustration Coloring by Mrs K

https://www.patreon.com/c/Kruggsmash
title: Short Forts: Putting sieges to the test
